import { Container, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap";
import MenuBlock from "./MenuBlock";
import Link from "next/link";

                      .split(" ")
                      .join("-")}`}

                  >
                    <MenuBlock index={option} title={option} />
                  </Link>
                </Col>
              );
            })}
          </Row>
        );
      })}
